Type Alias# Pixel_FF

iOSiPadOSMac CatalystmacOStvOSvisionOSwatchOS

```
typealias Pixel_FF = (Float, Float)
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/Accelerate/Pixel_FF#discussion)

A two-channel, single precision floating-point per channel pixel.

The channel order is generally given by the function that consumes the value.

## [See Also](/documentation/Accelerate/Pixel_FF#see-also)
